node.text: When I don’t see a way, I know with God there's always a way. When I don't see what I want to see, because of the faithfulness of God, I will choose to walk by faith. When I don't understand, I will believe with everything in me, My God is still good. I will worship Him before I see Him move. I will praise Him before I see Him act. Even in the waiting, I believe that He is good.
